thread.title_full: New MSU T-shirt cuts UM fans a little deeper

author: detroitnews.com
title: New MSU T-shirt cuts UM fans a little deeper
text:
The Michigan State-themed T-shirt commemorating the team's win over Michigan. (Photo: Represent) 
While the wound Saturday's shocking 27-21 loss is still fresh, this latest garment won't be used by Michigan fans to cauterize it.
The licensed T-shirt by crowd-selling merchandiser Represent sticks the sharpest edge a little deeper. Emblazoned on the front, "10 Seconds Left. Down 2. 0.2% Chances of Winning. The Game is Not Over Until We Say It Is."
Ouch.
The shirt is $24.99 is available at
represent.com
